<body>
    <h1>Chimichurri Chicken</h1>

    <p>
        Chimichurri Chicken is a delicious and flavorful grilled chicken dish marinated in a vibrant green sauce called chimichurri. The chimichurri sauce is made with fresh herbs, garlic, vinegar, and olive oil, which infuses the chicken with incredible flavors.
    </p>

    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>4 boneless, skinless chicken breasts</li>
        <li>1 cup fresh parsley leaves, finely chopped</li>
        <li>1/4 cup fresh cilantro leaves, finely chopped</li>
        <li>3 cloves garlic, minced</li>
        <li>2 tablespoons red wine vinegar</li>
        <li>1/2 cup extra virgin olive oil</li>
        <li>1 teaspoon dried oregano</li>
        <li>1/2 teaspoon red pepper flakes</li>
        <li>Salt and black pepper to taste</li>
    </ul>

